               <p>All intellectual property rights, including copyright, trademarks, and other proprietary rights, belong to <strong>Himalayan Hikers</strong>. You may not reproduce, distribute, modify, transmit, display, perform, or create derivative works of any Content without our prior written permission.</p>
               <h3>2. Limited Use</h3>
